The paper deals with the problem of capacity management in data centers, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also involves optimization techniques and algorithms, which could fall under Information Theory (cs.IT) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The use of convex functions in the objective function could also relate to Probability (cs.PF) and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
